==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Divinize
<hw>Div"i*nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To invest with a
divine character; to deify.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>M.
Arnold.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Man had <qex>divinized</qex> all those objects of awe.</q>
<rj><qau>Milman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Divisibility</ent>⟦br⟧
